{"tid":442553,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］其實人蠢唔緊要  最緊要唔好扮醒","createTime":"2017-10-20T17:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T16:59:05.000Z","uid":90505,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4ee58d3d209ff4ea4bd6ab3066b26ff700b679","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"一個人蠢 而且有自知之明<br />\n絕對冇問題 我可以理解 <br />\n雖然都會塞好多舊屎比自己食<br />\n<br />\n但蠢既以為好醒<br />\n成日做埋啲on9冇腦野<br />\n要人地硬食既真係好撚慘<br />\n仲要哂時間同佢辯駁<br />\n但永遠覺得自己巴撚閉<br />\n實情做野講野成個智障咁<br />\n呢啲唔止要自己受哂<br />\n仲要睇住佢懶醒既咀臉<br />\n屌你老母真係好令人好崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同意<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔同意"},{"pid":"72cee125b3ae986b3607944496916ef565c24c55","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"最慘屋企有個咁既人<br />\n日日對住真係人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e796020ca5915c1ac8bf13b04021255d8e4cf07","tid":442553,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"例子呢？"},{"pid":"55e1855dc229783550be959e2ab1a217a9fa821b","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例子呢？</blockquote><br />\n有好多生活鎖碎野可以搞到自己精神崩潰<br />\n例如一出街成日大驚小怪<br />\n一啲理應係人都知既野佢就當發現新大陸咁<br />\n<br />\n解決問題永遠都唔係用最有效既方法<br />\n<br />\n有次屋企有虱<br />\n佢就走去買埋啲唔知乜煙黎點<br />\n每晚訓覺就關哂啲窗門<br />\n搞到成間屋啲煙濃到以為著咗火<br />\n重點係啲煙臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沖完涼經過廳到番入房<br />\n講緊果幾秒 果陣味已經入哂啲衫褲頭髮入面<br />\n果次出街 同男朋友一見面就問我做乜咁大陣煙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常應該係用煙霧滅虱果啲<br />\n點都唔係一黎就搵啲咁既野黎搞呀<br />\n同佢講佢又永遠唔覺自己有問題<br />\n好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6342943a76ac1ac71437930ad3b01dac1f8a615","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"係味開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc28e15640a9a32bfb450a14c4503d89de009719","tid":442553,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"蠢人唔會知自己蠢<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"980b557e059b64ac21b10cd3bbc8a76558fbdf70","tid":442553,"uid":60231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"樓主點判斷自己唔係e類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70cca1410ebe2ae3a06f02236721a0b857074b1","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主點判斷自己唔係e類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼自己唔識既野唔會衝出黎柒先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968fb25fb98ff16478d519f109e563038fb6f941","tid":442553,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"我老母就係"},{"pid":"b347b0d2f29a8735b1f384390b03b2a4a62b6147","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蠢人唔會知自己蠢<br />\n此post已完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蠢但扮醒果啲就真心叫唔醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7075338bc8a40b0fe927fa5bc551397d7c889410","tid":442553,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老母就係</blockquote><br />\n我老母雖然讀書唔多 但好彩唔會扮醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24115d690328ddd017d10d7808a6c2924bae4a7b","tid":442553,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"連踩幾鑊地雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967fc6e1d2dd2f63ebb93341e5824e7908505714","tid":442553,"uid":3179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"出到去做野 大把呢類人<br />\n成日以為自己好撚醒<br />\n唔識又唔問 又錯 又要駁咀 籍口 多到傻<br />\n最大問題 係要執佢手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}